  "description": "Adding Kick Skills for EpicFight",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@pla_is_me\" title=\"YouTube\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761811663/youtube_icon_bcbanf.png\" alt=\"YouTube\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/EsvPsnqJpz\" title=\"Discord\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761811736/discord_icon_bg_rp4omx.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/pla_is_me\" title=\"Ko‑fi\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761815764/kofi_icon_bg_sy3foi.png\" alt=\"Ko‑fi\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/PlaIsMe\" title=\"github\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761811682/github_icon_bg_wmtjei.png\" alt=\"Github\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n**EpicFight : Kick Skills** is a mod split from the Annoying Villagers 1.4 mod. It adds a passive skill that allows you to kick with a new key bind and deal stamina damage, moreover, when you're guard break or stunned you can press kick again to escape.\n\nA configuration file is included, allowing you to modify the kick stamina deal value.\n\nThe stamina damage mechanism only works on Player and Combat Evolution mobs.",
